{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "15.0",
      "line_index": 15,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "26fdf8ee",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ここに伝説の霊薬が……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5ab06eb5",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "うん……！　今度こそ霊薬を手に入れたいです……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2fd4b593",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナに頼まれ、伝説の霊薬がある洞窟にやってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d36c5baf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "前回一人で来た時は探索に失敗して",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.2",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d36c5baf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "引き返す事になったと言っていたが、その原因は話してくれなかった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.0",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "24d4de65",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でも何て言うか……雰囲気があるな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.2",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "24d4de65",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "前回来た時はここに一人で入ったの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7c7931ee",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "そうですよ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.2",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7c7931ee",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "ちょっと怖かったですけど、霊薬がどうしても欲しくて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8f34ce15",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "勇気があるんだな、ミキュナは。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.2",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8f34ce15",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "よし、それじゃあ今度こそその霊薬を手に入れような",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dce20384",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "うんっ！　お兄さんがいれば絶対に手に入れられるはずですっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.0",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e041e5f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "洞窟に入ると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.2",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e041e5f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "岩が剥き出しのジメジメした薄暗い空間が目の前に広がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1aec07a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかししばらく歩を進めると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.2",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1aec07a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "石造りの明らかに人工物である通路にたどり着く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.0",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4bf8f99b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんか雰囲気変わったな……洞窟って言うよりもダンジョンって感じ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "67da8a6a",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "地図の通りです……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.2",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "67da8a6a",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "このダンジョンを越えた先に霊薬があるはずですっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4bb4e149",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ……！　走ったら危ないって！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9447933",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナは興奮を抑えられないのか、小走りにダンジョンを駆ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4f49aab2",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "あれ～……？　地図だとこの先に道があるはずなのですけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "36e03968",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "行き止まりだな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.0",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "587dcdd7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "角を曲がると目の前に広がる一面の壁。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c287a179",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "道らしき道も見つからず二人で立ち尽くす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.0",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29841a9d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "道間違えたってことはない……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fe5eb0cb",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "うーん……間違えてはいないと思いますけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.3",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "fe5eb0cb",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "きゃうっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.0",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "367d4fa7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、危ないっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "737f77ff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナは石に躓き、身を守る様に壁に手をつく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4467e54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すると壁がガラガラと音を立て穴が開いてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.0",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e30bc75c",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "はうううっ！　み、道ありました……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.2",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e30bc75c",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "この先に道がありますっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d59b5d3c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そう、か……ところで大丈夫？　頭とかぶつけなかった？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9129e9b3",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "大丈夫ですっ、特にどこかにぶつけては……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.4",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "9129e9b3",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "あ、あれ……？か、身体がすっぽりハマって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.6",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 6,
      "line_hash": "9129e9b3",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "う、動けないですぅ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "101.0",
      "line_index": 101,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8657672c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え？　マジ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16f0c3bf",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "ま、まじ、ですぅ……！　ううう、腰引っ掛かって……あうっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5533d5c1",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "待ってて、すぐにどうにかするから……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c4e0ac19",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "慌ててミキュナの周りの壁を叩いてみるが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.2",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c4e0ac19",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "とてもじゃないが素手で壊れそうにない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.0",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5e4f8382",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "たまたまミキュナが押したところだけが",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.2",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5e4f8382",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "脆くなってしまっていたみたいだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.0",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5e31af1f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ちょっと待っててくれ、何か壁壊せるもの探してくるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "122.0",
      "line_index": 122,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "902bb267",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "は、はい～……お手間お掛けしますぅ～……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "372a4f16",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そうミキュナに伝えたものの、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.2",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "372a4f16",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の視線はある一点に注がれてしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.0",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "41e417f6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（カワイイお尻だな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.2",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "41e417f6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "小ぶりだけど丸みがあって肉付きが良くて……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6a4146dc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（い、いかんいかん……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.2",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6a4146dc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺はこんな時にいったい何を考えているんだ……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "134.0",
      "line_index": 134,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5503dd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナの壁尻の姿に胸がヘンに高鳴る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "de0d8fb8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少しくらいなら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.2",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "de0d8fb8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな邪な願望がそっと目の前のお尻に手を伸ばしてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a7c3d635",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "──ひゃうっ！？　だ、誰……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.2",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a7c3d635",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "ま、まさかこの前の触手さんっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.0",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ef1f94c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（触手……？　触っているの俺だって気がついていない……？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d45950dd",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "こんな時にダメですぅ……！　お兄さんが戻ってきちゃいますぅ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f933381",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（もしかして前回探索に失敗したのって、その触手が原因……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.2",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9f933381",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "触手に襲われて……そ、それなら言えないわけだよな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9d1829b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でもこれって……このまま続けても勘違いしてくれるんじゃ……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.2",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d9d1829b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "だ、ダメだダメだ……！　いったい何を考えているんだ俺は……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "156.0",
      "line_index": 156,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "908d6f51",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（すぐにミキュナを助け出さないと……そうしないと……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "20113ad8",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "──ひぎぃ！？　んあ、う、ううう……！！　だ、ダメぇ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "173.0",
      "line_index": 173,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96a4cc47",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突然の挿入に驚きの声をあげるミキュナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4761e12d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "苦しそうな声をあげ、動けない身体で必死に逃れようともがく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e1737b41",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "うう……ダメ、ですぅ……お兄さんに見られちゃいますぅ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "33a743ba",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（お、俺はなんてことを……！　動けない女の子に一方的に……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.0",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1d695a8a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すぐに肉棒を抜かないと、そう思うものの、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.0",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb8f6715",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナの僅かに湿った狭い膣の心地良さに動けずにいた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2237a2a5",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "どうしてこんなときに触手さんが……んぅぅぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.2",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2237a2a5",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "ぬ、抜いて……くださいぃ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.4",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "2237a2a5",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "もうあそこイジメないでくださいぃ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.0",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91e32523",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナの声に背徳感を覚え、ヘンに興奮が高ぶる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.0",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1733c127",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒が狭い膣の中で何度も跳ねあがり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.2",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1733c127",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナの小さなお尻がビクンと反応する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.0",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8622e933",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "うう……わたし、初めてなのに……それなのにこんな形で……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.2",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8622e933",
      "speaker": "ミキュナ",
      "ja": "初めてはお兄さんにって決めていたのにぃ……あうっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.0",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "265497f4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ミキュナのそんな告白に俺の胸がさらに高鳴る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.0",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 0,
